Still some stuff are made by hand.

This should be solved in some point.

After compile crosstool-ng , it should be compiled TAO

Load bash_profile.cross.acs 

source bash_profile.cross.acs

To compile TAO, it is mandatory copy those files:

cp platform_macros.GNU $(ACSROOT)/../TAO/ACE_wrappers/build/linux/include/makeinclude/platform_macros.GNU
cp config.h $(ACSROOT)/../TAO/ACE_wrappers/build/linux/ace/config.h
cp platform_linux_common.GNU $(ACSROOT)/../TAO/ACE_wrappers/include/makeinclude/platform_linux_common.GNU
cp platform_linux.GNU $(ACSROOT)/../TAO/ACE_wrappers/include/makeinclude/platform_linux.GNU


Then compile in this order:

cd $ACE_ROOT/TAO/tao ; make -j4
cd $ACE_ROOT/TAO/orbsvcs; make -j4
cd $ACE_ROOT/TAO/utils; make -j4
